---
layout: base.njk
title: Land Rover Servicing FAQs | Stuart Gilbert Landrovers, Kent
metaDescription: Common questions about Land Rover servicing, repairs, costs, models and booking at our independent specialist workshop in Sittingbourne, Kent. Call 01795 843116.
permalink: /faq/
preloadFonts:
  - /fonts/fraunces-latin-var.woff2
---
<section class="prose-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="tag">FAQ</div>
      <h2>Questions we're often asked.</h2>
      <p>If your question isn't answered here, the quickest thing is to give the workshop a ring on <a href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}" style="color:var(--brand);border-bottom:1px solid var(--accent)">{{ site.phoneDisplay }}</a> — you'll speak to Stuart or David.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      {%- for item in faq | confirmed %}
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>{{ item.q }}</h3>
        <p>{{ item.a }}</p>
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {%- for item in faq | confirmed %}
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": {{ item.q | dump | safe }},
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": {{ item.a | dump | safe }} }
    }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
    {%- endfor %}
  ]
}
</script>
